ing: 1 (20 ounce) can crushed pineapple with juice
1 (3 ounce) package instant lemon pudding mix
des: "This pie is very easy to make and is always a big hit."
ins: In a medium bowl, combine pineapple with juice, pudding mix, and sour cream. Mix well and spoon into graham cracker crust. Chill before serving.
